# Test simple if expression
parse 'if $x > 0 { true }'
---
> Program:
>   [  0] Statement::If
>     condition:
>       Expr::Binary(Gt)
>         left:
>           Expr::Variable($x)
>         right:
>           Expr::Literal(Integer(0))
>     then:
>       [  0] Statement::Expression
>         Expr::Literal(Bool(true))
>
